short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds codechef problems to a list

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you solving problems on CodeChef but don't find any way to save/bookmark tough problems for future reference. 
Here it is! Codechef Archive enables you to save the link to your favorite CodeChef problem and store it in your Entensions-tray. All you have to do is to install this extension, and it does the rest.
